{"tid":1821950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「手足」 陳梓維又出醜","createTime":"2020-01-12T15:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T05:49:25.000Z","uid":1426,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e50aaa4c353dd0b61f09aee5d243315cee82f1","tid":1821950,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"「三無青年」（無政黨背景、無從政經驗、無高學歷）、油尖旺區議員陳梓維又再為大家帶來笑話！《蘋果日報》日前採訪這位三無青年，以紀錄片方式拍攝他當選後的情況。記者要求陳梓維寫出「逆轉佐敦藍」五個字時，他居然不懂得怎樣寫，要靠手機語音識別「逆轉」兩字怎樣寫，但最後仍然寫錯，場面相當尷尬。訪問中，陳梓維再度把自己會考零分、毅進不合格掛在嘴邊，似乎十分樂於將此作為突出個人形象的標誌。有市民在網上留言稱「睇嚇呢個白痴區議員呢四年點過」；不過有「手足」好「有愛」，說「弱智都係手足，唔割」。<br />\n鄭晴認為，這一幕「再世倉頡陳梓維造字」時刻，確實吸睛，蘋果記者居然要會考零分的陳梓維寫這麼多筆畫的字詞，存心「靠害」的意圖似乎好明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8rRHc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8rRHc4.jpg&h=5209b8e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a754dc269305c826d817700f36f823ab27f206f1","tid":1821950,"uid":14337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"可能有讀寫障礙"},{"pid":"eff9a7b2223d2c1d28894f75cc47454c2de5ab3d","tid":1821950,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"2個字都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814c87a30095949a02298b16c78ba71cf3661872","tid":1821950,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"@爵連"},{"pid":"44bd1a5607b86cb039442f8fa972fca8a114e63e","tid":1821950,"uid":1734,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"唉 呢d 去洗碗都唔請啦"},{"pid":"3badf4f134083e49a42bc9264e4043a04bea8ad0","tid":1821950,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"我見到 車車迷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7054ae7d53c5ad3b7d13156eae2a1c40bbc8719","tid":1821950,"ui